{"tid":328500,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"9個出生入死好兄弟 定 1個賢良淑德靚老婆 ?","createTime":"2017-07-19T15:25:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T15:39:16.000Z","uid":61443,"like":5,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"01bfb65b44f59e966a5fa58bb722802896398522","tid":328500,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:25:09.000Z","msg":"9個唔係親兄弟<br />\n但係一條心上戰場<br />\n同甘共苦生死與共<br />\n<br />\n1個靚老婆<br />\n入得廚房出得廳堂<br />\n相夫教子孝順父母<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正評 九兄弟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負評 好老婆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59dbdd16907f1405a44a72dd81311f41da5e46b1","tid":328500,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:25:46.000Z","msg":"十兄弟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b05c23e6a6e37a7d0c9462ebf2e8bdd5a7afb9b","tid":328500,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:26:27.000Z","msg":"..."},{"pid":"74503d6578a7d9d0c76290ce16385ed237b045ae","tid":328500,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:29:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十兄弟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n假設你係外國<br />\n同9個fd一齊打仗 （香港太和平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n聽人講過<br />\n上個戰場既隊友<br />\n仲親過親生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad18dd84431ecccb88037108715d78de485d947b","tid":328500,"uid":31318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:30:53.000Z","msg":"Why not both"},{"pid":"5ff764590fe95dcd3a684140ea8ca2028d9f0575","tid":328500,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:32:54.000Z","msg":"諗諗下好似開錯topic<br />\n而家好似講緊你想要邊樣咁<br />\n即係由冇到有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n應該設定<br />\n你2樣都擁有 <br />\n而你覺得邊樣重要啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738b89fdde459df2685e7d17ac66339b3314b49e","tid":328500,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:34:32.000Z","msg":"成件事係咁<br />\n<br />\n話說我識左個外國人<br />\n佢一係講佢9個兄弟<br />\n一係講佢老婆 <br />\n<br />\n感覺到佢2樣都好重視 <br />\n所以想睇下大家意見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485fdadf811f9bb48eff167c01b93ac919052eab","tid":328500,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:39:16.000Z","msg":"細佬既揀選 （心中地位）<br />\n<br />\n如果由冇到有 <br />\n可能會揀老婆<br />\n始終同你一世人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係如果經歷過<br />\n應該會揀9兄弟 <br />\n因為冇佢9個<br />\n你條命應該冇左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}